  "detailed_description": "<strong>Auro The Bunny</strong> is a charming 2D platformer where you control Auro, a fearless rabbit, who must collect all the fruits scattered across the levels. This task will require a lot of patience and precision from the player, and the game can get dark pretty quickly... Get ready to face various obstacles and challenges!<br><br><strong>Challenges</strong><br>Face numerous challenges that will test your dexterity, reflexes, and most likely your sanity...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/f493e4d4e1fc27a417635c5d7c760acc.poster.avif?t=1737761276\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/f493e4d4e1fc27a417635c5d7c760acc.webm?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/f493e4d4e1fc27a417635c5d7c760acc.mp4?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Challenging Obstacles</strong><br>Avoid a variety of dangerous obstacles that stand in your way. Use your wits to overcome these adversities.<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/8280644d5a118e315e1f689a87f01d6e.poster.avif?t=1737761276\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/8280644d5a118e315e1f689a87f01d6e.webm?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/8280644d5a118e315e1f689a87f01d6e.mp4?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Three Distinct Scenarios</strong><br>Traverse different environments while tackling challenges with Auro the bunny.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/2ffd0be292d1029450711559bf1f19a5.poster.avif?t=1737761276\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/2ffd0be292d1029450711559bf1f19a5.webm?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825180/extras/2ffd0be292d1029450711559bf1f19a5.mp4?t=1737761276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Enchanting Soundtrack</strong><br>Enjoy a beautiful soundtrack as you accompany Auro on his journey.",
